structured.description: A `MockAccountID` class that extends the `AccountID` class and is used for testing purposes. It takes a user ID, account properties, and a protocol name as inputs and initializes an instance of the `MockAccountID` class with those values. The class provides a way to create an account ID for a provider user ID and account properties without changing the account UID when the server has changed.

items.description: Extends AccountID and creates an account ID for a provider user ID and account properties, loading the account value from the account properties to prevent changing the account UID when the server changes.
items.name: MockAccountID
